make videos for God’s eyes only.","genre_ids":[18,35],"popularity":0.1318,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/lqmUNSPLrexFxktbSlzitonzQq6.jpg","release_date":"2022-12-05","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/vIyCxNPfXxRl2ManxDGoD4SWaaz.jpg","original_title":"Influence","original_language":"en"},{"id":671780,"adult":false,"title":"Alberto and the Concrete Jungle","video":false,"overview":"Al B. is a modern nomad. He's a photojournalist who lives alone on the road and idolizes Indiana Jones, spending his free time searching for fun adventures to get involved in. The world is his playground. As soon as he makes a new friend, he's saying goodbye, off to a new destination. But leaving NYC proves absurdly difficult when a corrupt employer decides to hold him down. Al's attempts to find a way out lead him across NYC's 5 boroughs, forcing him to deal with various colorful characters that further complicate the process and, in some cases, make him question his nomadic lifestyle altogether.","genre_ids":[18,35,12],"popularity":0.1494,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/edaaEnkS7oAQroZxNk8mbxreYMZ.jpg","release_date":"2020-10-21","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Alberto and the Concrete Jungle","original_language":"en"},{"id":470926,"adult":false,"title":"Litterbugs","video":false,"overview":"Helped by her self-made flying mechanical creatures, a young inventor and an enigmatic pint-sized superhero defeat the town bullies and find an unexpected friendship.","genre_ids":[10751,12,35],"popularity":2.2533,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/c9R08jCwjt6fTRoUHr2ezoWzJ4G.jpg","release_date":"2016-01-01","vote_average":8,"backdrop_path":"/kM1AUPVQgizpi80vlaWIBeeexKW.jpg","original_title":"Litterbugs","original_language":"en"},{"id":1261876,"adult":false,"title":"Influencer","video":false,"overview":"Karen, a young woman obsessed with the most influential influencer of the moment, Kamilah Kay, decides to undergo surgery to look like her. Seeing how well the new Karen is received