ks a hidden agenda fuelled by the arrival of a privileged young yuppie.","genre_ids":[80,18,53],"popularity":0.562,"vote_count":95,"poster_path":"/8xYm5fZXT0DNuGRUHdkQJ1puNYH.jpg","release_date":"2021-09-10","vote_average":6.058,"backdrop_path":"/n000l23aqkqt4k6NQz5UeaLNN25.jpg","original_title":"Small Engine Repair","original_language":"en"},{"id":464678,"adult":false,"title":"The Rachels","video":false,"overview":"After a popular teen falls to her death, her best friend basks in the glow of the social media attention, while their rival seeks to avenge the past and uncover the truth behind the mysterious death.","genre_ids":[18,10770,80],"popularity":0.4223,"vote_count":33,"poster_path":"/M1iRgIT4gWbnZYzX0SMfy6cEwW.jpg","release_date":"2017-01-15","vote_average":5.9,"backdrop_path":"/d60dGbuOCeLCWmuatLUOkDD8w8W.jpg","original_title":"The Rachels","original_language":"en"},{"id":1455254,"adult":false,"title":"Toy Vlog Hunt","video":false,"overview":"Just a regular toy vlogger stalking the aisles of your local store as usual, beware.","genre_ids":[27,35],"popularity":0.1879,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/pz8ghUIdLcghfV96DhRRPgVuwq.jpg","release_date":"2025-03-29","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Toy Vlog Hunt","original_language":"en"},{"id":656770,"adult":false,"title":"The Columnist","video":false,"overview":"An opinion columnist and author, subjected to constant misogynistic abuse on social media, snaps and goes on a killing spree against her online abusers.","genre_ids":[35,27,10770],"popularity":0.5115,"vote_count":58,"poster_path":"/sCPSdas3h9osgHiNhWGjCOYU5Bb.jpg","release_date":"2019-12-20","vote_average":5.6,"backdrop_path":"/gfcTTHQTNU4gyHbtuu6cubgAcaB.jpg","original_title":"De Kuthoer","original_language":"nl"},{"id":656690,"adult":false,"title":"The Social Dilemma","video":false,"overview":"This documentary-drama hybrid explores the dangerous human impact of social networking, with tech experts sounding the alarm on their own creati